Clean localhost SSL
===================

# Install

1. Append your domains to the "domains" files (one by line)
2. Generate root cert with `src/generate-root-cert.sh`
3. Add root cert to trusted Authorities of your browser
3. Generate domains cert with `src/generate-domains.sh`

# Update

1. Append your domains to the "domains" files (one by line)
3. Generate domains cert with `src/generate-domains.sh`
